{"tid":2119924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何志平服刑回港後首於報章撰文　批西方國家熱昏了頭、傾力打壓","createTime":"2020-07-22T11:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T14:06:03.000Z","uid":36494,"like":17,"dislike":135,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"fef70065e02807f5ea889bf1032b518e12b423c2","tid":2119924,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:10:53.000Z","msg":"前民政事務局局長何志平去年因向非洲國家政要行賄罪成，被美國法院判囚三年，上月初刑滿出獄後，被遣返香港。他為《東方日報》撰寫專欄，今日（22日）首次刊出。他在文中藉談論天氣評論時局，指西方國家「熱昏了的頭腦」、「步步追擊，處處為營，全面封殺，傾力打壓」，而東方則清涼、「沉着應對，見招拆招」，希望未來各國能共享「冷暖適應」的環境。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">他指環觀全球局勢，西方是「熱昏了的頭腦」，「步步追擊，處處為營，全面封殺，傾力打壓」，反觀東方則清涼、能「沉着應對，見招拆招，尊嚴的反駁，負責的承擔」，西方與東方形成強烈對比。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%95%E5%BF%97%E5%B9%B3%E6%9C%8D%E5%88%91%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E5%BE%8C%E9%A6%96%E6%96%BC%E5%A0%B1%E7%AB%A0%E6%92%B0%E6%96%87-%E6%89%B9%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%86%B1%E6%98%8F%E4%BA%86%E9%A0%AD-%E5%82%BE%E5%8A%9B%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%2588%2591%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E6%2592%25B0%25E6%2596%2587-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%2586%25B1%25E6%2598%258F%25E4%25BA%2586%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E5%2582%25BE%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=50dd78f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%2588%2591%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E6%2592%25B0%25E6%2596%2587-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%2586%25B1%25E6%2598%258F%25E4%25BA%2586%25E9%25A0%25